            <p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="1">I'd like to hear what all the Wizzies have to say.  You know, since they all swore their lives that VI would never nerf MB.  I think the way they're setting it up will be good.  Sounds fair for everyone <br />
<br />
CH - Don't think the change will be significant enough to notice.  What's the average top-end tank look like, 8-9k hp?  If you get down to a point where a CH isn't a CH, then I think the problem is the cleric, not the spell.<br />
<br />
I hope this change to monks satisfies the warriors</font></p>
             
