            <p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="1">The nerf bat is still swinging.. bite thy tongue. <br />
<br />
The only nerf so far I don't actually agree with is the monk change. In history (RL as well as lore) Monks are martial artists. Martial artists are supposed to have a stronger ability to handle combat situations. Martial art is a skill that is overall better than any other combat skill. In any encounter I have seen someone using martial arts comes out with less damage than the guy using brawn as his means of combat.</font></p>
             
